"2:186:17" : {s: 2, a: 186, w: 17, r: "رشد", t: "يَرْشُدُونَ", l: "يَرْشُدُ", lc: 1, tl: "yarshudūna", lb: "পথ দেখানো",e: "(be) led aright", b: "সত্যের সন্ধান পাবে", i: "mereka mendapat petunjuk/kebenaran", f: 1, rm: "to follow the right way, be well guided or directed, true direction, correct rule of action, straight forwardness, maturity of a child/intellect, capacity to manage ones affairs."},
